title: Using \dotfill in LaTex

Adding a line of dots in [[LaTeX]]

Something like this using `\dotfill`

```
\noindent Item One\dotfill $1,000  
\noindent Item Two \dotfill $1,000  
\noindent Item Three \dotfill $10,000  
```

Gives me something like this:

